headline.main: Florida Deputy Hurt Breaking Up Fight After Soccer Game
headline.print_headline: Florida Deputy Hurt Breaking Up Fight After Soccer Game

lead_paragraph: Authorities say a Florida sheriff's deputy is recovering after he was injured while trying to break up a fight between fans after the Orlando City Soccer game.
